{{spanish name 2|L<U+00F3>pez|Bilbao}}
'''Iv<U+00E1>n Guido L<U+00F3>pez Bilbao''' (born 10 March 1990) is a [[Chile]]an athlete specialising in the [[middle-distance running|middle-distance events]].<ref>{{iaaf name|228808}}</ref> He won several medals on regional level.

